OL,3,CSunderland striker opens up about
OL,4,Calcohol addiction
OL,6,FSunderland striker Aaron Connolly has
OL,7,Fopened up about his battle with
OL,8,Falcohol addiction and how he feels
OL,9,Fpeople view him as a "waste of
OL,10,Fpotential".
OL,12,FThe Republic of Ireland international
OL,13,Fhas spoken to his new club's media
OL,14,Fteam about how his personality changed
OL,15,Fsince bursting onto the Premier League
OL,16,Fstage with two goals on his first
OL,17,Fstart for Brighton.
OL,19,FThe 24-year-old said: "It was one of
OL,20,Fthe best days of my life but also one
OL,21,Fof the worst as well.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
