OL,3,CSunderland striker opens up about
OL,4,Calcohol addiction
OL,6,F"I stopped working. I stopped doing
OL,7,Fthe things that I should have kept
OL,8,Fdoing. I started to believe the hype
OL,9,Fand I didn't turn into a good person
OL,10,Fafter that.
OL,12,F"It got to a point where the buzz was
OL,13,Fmore from drinking alcohol than going
OL,14,Fout on a football pitch.
OL,16,F"I used to look forward to the games
OL,17,Ffinishing so I could have time to go
OL,18,Fand have a drink."
