OL,3,CSunderland striker opens up about
OL,4,Calcohol addiction
OL,6,FConnolly made 45 appearances for top-
OL,7,Fflight Brighton before spending time
OL,8,Fon loan at Middlesbrough and in Venice.
OL,10,FHe signed for Sunderland from Hull for
OL,11,Fthe 24/25 season but is yet to make a
OL,12,Ffirst-team appearance.
OL,14,FAsked how people would describe him,
OL,15,Fhe said: "I know the perception of me
OL,16,Fisn't the best, I'm not blind to that.
OL,18,F"I think a lot of people would say
OL,19,Farrogant and a waste of potential. But
OL,20,Fthe people close to me, they know what
OL,21,FI'm like."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
