OL,4,Calcohol addiction
OL,6,FConnolly said it was after two goals
OL,7,Fagainst Tottenham Hotspur that things
OL,8,Fstarted to turn.
OL,10,F"I started to live the lifestyle of a
OL,11,Ffootballer without the football side
OL,12,Fof it. I just let myself believe
OL,13,Feverything that people were saying
OL,14,Fonline."
OL,16,FDespite scoring eight goals in 28
OL,17,Fappearances at Hull City last season,
OL,18,FConnolly says his life was a mess off
OL,19,Fthe pitch and he decided to check
OL,20,Fhimself into a treatment clinic over
OL,21,Fthe summer.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
