OL,3,CSunderland striker opens up about
OL,4,Calcohol addiction
OL,6,FAsked why he wanted to tell his story,
OL,7,FConnolly said he wished that he had
OL,8,Fheard about an active footballer who
OL,9,Fhad taken a break in their career.
OL,11,FHe said: "I feel like I owe people. I
OL,12,Fhad everything that any young boy
OL,13,Fwould dream of and I couldn't get hold
OL,14,Fof my addiction.
OL,16,F"It's not just park bench vodka bottle
OL,17,Fpeople, anybody can be affected by it."
