OL,3,CSunderland striker opens up about
OL,4,Calcohol addiction
OL,6,FThe forward's road to recovery
OL,7,Fcontinued with an appearance and goal
OL,8,Fin an under-21s game against Derby
OL,9,FCounty on 7 October.
OL,11,FOn his attempts to break into
OL,12,FSunderland's first team to help their
OL,13,Fpromotion bid, he said: "I feel
OL,14,Frefreshed. I feel like that young kid
OL,15,Fwho came to England again.
OL,17,F"I've got a purpose. My goal is to get
OL,18,Fthis club to the Premier League."
