OL,6,FConnolly's story being shared by the
OL,7,Fclub on social media has been widely
OL,8,Fwell received.
OL,10,FThe Roker Report said: "Let's all get
OL,11,Fbehind Aaron and wish him well as he
OL,12,Fhopefully kickstarts his career at
OL,13,FSunderland."
OL,15,FAnyone reading this article who feels
OL,16,Fthey could benefit with talking to
OL,17,Fsomeone, can see a list of alcohol
OL,18,Faddiction helplines on the ITV website.
